687
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:53,760
[SPEAKER_01] pokazala da ih volim, poštem i sve ostalo,

688
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] da ja trebam djeliti poklone njima.

689
00:41:55,579 --> 00:41:58,440
[SPEAKER_01] I onda oni nisu baš oduševljeni,

690
00:41:58,440 --> 00:42:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] još me ono pošpotaju kaj si trošila novce.

691
00:42:01,699 --> 00:42:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imamo i onaj još jedan podjezik nekakve ljubave.

692
00:42:07,380 --> 00:42:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] Imam poklone, imam te nekakve,

693
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad one drugi radi nekakva dijela za tebe.

694
00:42:13,039 --> 00:42:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je toliko divno u srcu,

695
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:17,699
[SPEAKER_01] naprimjer kad neko iz moje obitelji

696
00:42:17,699 --> 00:42:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] napravi nešto za što joj nisam dala nalog.

697
00:42:20,599 --> 00:42:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] To me isto ispuni ljubavlju i poštovanjem.

698
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] A naprimjer mom Danielu,

699
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] on voli nagdodir, voli zagrljaj,

700
00:42:30,659 --> 00:42:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] a men to ne treba.

701
00:42:32,119 --> 00:42:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] I men to tako nelogično.

702
00:42:33,699 --> 00:42:36,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj bomo sad od toga dobili?

703
00:42:36,519 --> 00:42:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dajmo neke pomoći si,

704
00:42:38,059 --> 00:42:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo si kupit nekaj i to će biti to.

705
00:42:40,380 --> 00:42:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo malo zamjerili uloge tu.

706
00:42:42,079 --> 00:42:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer voli riječi pohvale

707
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] i kad nešto primijetiš,

708
00:42:49,039 --> 00:42:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaj dobro napravimo,

709
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:52,039
[SPEAKER_01] a mi žene dat pohvalu za nekaj,

710
00:42:52,039 --> 00:42:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] ono, zaka bi sad ga pohvalili za nekaj

711
