[SPEAKER_01] kaj skuham ručak ili operam veš?

715
00:42:59,019 --> 00:43:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] Niko.

716
00:43:00,059 --> 00:43:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ili daje možda,

717
00:43:02,039 --> 00:43:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] ali ono, kao,

718
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne trebam ga reći

719
00:43:03,960 --> 00:43:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] da mora zamijeniti, ne znam,

720
00:43:05,119 --> 00:43:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] poklopac na školjci.

721
00:43:06,139 --> 00:43:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] To je normalno, to zna.

722
00:43:07,260 --> 00:43:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] Alo, trebamo reći.

723
00:43:09,679 --> 00:43:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Trebamo primijeti da su napravili nešto,

724
00:43:12,460 --> 00:43:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] možda čak i bez da smo im rekli,

725
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] bez da smo im rekli šest puta,

726
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] možda tek i za drugog puta

727
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] smo napravili nešto.

728
00:43:19,059 --> 00:43:21,380
[SPEAKER_01] To, napredak.

729
00:43:21,380 --> 00:43:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je situacija,

730
00:43:23,059 --> 00:43:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] meni ne bilo jasno,

731
00:43:23,900 --> 00:43:24,699
