738
00:43:30,059 --> 00:43:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu niš rekle da su gladni.

739
00:43:34,860 --> 00:43:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, dobro.

740
00:43:37,159 --> 00:43:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, možeš se sad na to ljutiti,

741
