745
00:43:46,440 --> 00:43:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] ono, trebaš,

746
00:43:47,039 --> 00:43:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] trebamo jesti.

747
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi ti nešto jeo?

748
00:43:48,639 --> 00:43:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa jesam, oni su nisbi bili oko mene

749
00:43:50,239 --> 00:43:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] i nisu rekli da su gladni.

750
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ono, kad ti jedeš,

751
00:43:53,400 --> 00:43:54,860
