752
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] To ono nekak,

753
00:43:56,519 --> 00:43:57,599
[SPEAKER_01] što je normalno,

754
00:43:57,599 --> 00:43:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali moramo opet biti svjesni

755
00:43:58,519 --> 00:43:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] da smo mi ljudi,

756
00:43:59,380 --> 00:44:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] da imamo svakakve dane,

757
00:44:01,099 --> 00:44:03,599
[SPEAKER_01] mi pogotovo žene i dane u mjesecu

758
00:44:03,599 --> 00:44:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] i svašta nešto,

759
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:06,360
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su nas i osjećaj,

760
00:44:06,360 --> 00:44:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] sve nam je nešto napumpano.

761
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se i osjećamo tako.

762
00:44:10,760 --> 00:44:11,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tako onda i moškarac

763
00:44:11,619 --> 00:44:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] treba imati razumijevanja za to.

764
00:44:13,380 --> 00:44:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ja trebam imati razumijevanja za njegove,

765
00:44:15,139 --> 00:44:18,420
[SPEAKER_01] zato što mu nije važno sad bilo to nešto.

766
00:44:18,420 --> 00:44:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] Tu dolazimo do tih različitosti.

767
00:44:20,980 --> 00:44:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] Nemo misliti ako je meni važno

768
00:44:22,699 --> 00:44:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] im su pokloni,

769
