771
00:44:26,420 --> 00:44:28,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nisi primijetio što njemu važno

772
00:44:28,360 --> 00:44:30,719
[SPEAKER_01] da bi se sjećao poštovano i voljeno,

773
00:44:30,719 --> 00:44:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] pite ga.

774
00:44:31,460 --> 00:44:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo jednostavno.

775
00:44:33,420 --> 00:44:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] I stvari riješeno.

776
00:44:35,079 --> 00:44:37,780
[SPEAKER_01] I sjećat ćete se voljeno i poštovano

777
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] i bit će puno lakše prebroditi

778
00:44:39,880 --> 00:44:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] one sve situacije koje nas čekaju.

779
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, tips and tricks.

780
00:44:44,179 --> 00:44:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] U biti ovo ne razumiju da ja djecu

781
00:44:48,079 --> 00:44:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] nisam htio siliti sama da jedu.

782
00:44:49,900 --> 00:44:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo se razumijeli.

783
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta kad spominjamo brak

784
00:44:56,159 --> 00:44:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] i svatko će reći da je jedna

785
00:44:57,780 --> 00:44:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] od ključnih stvari u braku

786
00:44:59,360 --> 00:45:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] komunikacija.

787
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

788
00:45:02,800 --> 00:45:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] Definitivno.

789
00:45:03,739 --> 00:45:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Definitivno možemo reći da komunikacija

790
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:09,420
