793
00:45:12,320 --> 00:45:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] I o tome želimo progovoriti.

794
00:45:16,119 --> 00:45:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] Što mislite da se nađete vi, evo, govorimo hrvatski

795
00:45:20,179 --> 00:45:21,619
