796
00:45:21,619 --> 00:45:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Niti vi znate kineski,

797
00:45:23,360 --> 00:45:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] niti on zna hrvatski i vi lijepo komunicirate.

798
00:45:26,780 --> 00:45:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] Istina bi tu bile ruke, noge

799
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:29,820
[SPEAKER_00] u porabi, ali

800
00:45:29,820 --> 00:45:31,219
[SPEAKER_00] da li bi se vi razumijeli?

801
00:45:31,219 --> 00:45:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da li bi vi u konačnici

802
00:45:33,739 --> 00:45:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] i konačnici shvatili

803
00:45:34,739 --> 00:45:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] posljedice ako bi bilo nešto konkretno

804
00:45:36,340 --> 00:45:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] što bi trebalo dogovoriti?

805
00:45:37,519 --> 00:45:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što treba.

806
00:45:40,139 --> 00:45:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi.

807
00:45:41,079 --> 00:45:43,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi kao muškarci i žene

808
00:45:43,820 --> 00:45:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] imamo sasvim drugačije načine

809
00:45:46,559 --> 00:45:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] komunikacije i razumijevanja.

810
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi muškarci

811
00:45:50,159 --> 00:45:51,659
[SPEAKER_00] komuniciramo na jedan način,

812
00:45:51,659 --> 00:45:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] žene komuniciraju

813
00:45:53,139 --> 00:45:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] na jedan sasvim drugačiji način.

814
00:45:54,960 --> 00:45:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je njima logično,

815
00:45:57,579 --> 00:45:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] da vam ponekad...

816
00:45:58,980 --> 00:46:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kužim, pa učinio sam točno ono.

817
00:46:02,960 --> 00:46:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dječki, evo, muškarci,

818
00:46:05,760 --> 00:46:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] jeste ikad napravili nalog supruge

819
00:46:09,960 --> 00:46:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] i onda je bilo nešto poput

820
00:46:11,920 --> 00:46:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja to tebi nisam rekla.

821
00:46:13,860 --> 00:46:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onak, molim,

822
00:46:17,619 --> 00:46:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] pa to je tako si poslao poruku.

823
00:46:20,159 --> 00:46:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nisam to mislila.

824
00:46:21,559 --> 00:46:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako nisam to mislila?

825
00:46:23,000 --> 00:46:23,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to piše.

826
00:46:23,820 --> 00:46:26,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je velika razlika

827
00:46:26,239 --> 00:46:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] između muškarca i žene

828
00:46:27,719 --> 00:46:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] što mi uopće nemamo

829
00:46:30,019 --> 00:46:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] isti jezik ljubavi u smislu toga,

830
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:33,679
[SPEAKER_00] isti jezik komunikacije.

831
00:46:33,679 --> 00:46:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što je jedna od najvećih pogrešaka

832
00:46:37,099 --> 00:46:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] kad pričamo komunikacije,

833
00:46:38,519 --> 00:46:39,440
[SPEAKER_00] što mi smatramo,

834
00:46:39,440 --> 00:46:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] da bi nas drugi razumijeli

835
00:46:41,659 --> 00:46:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] i da bi ta komunikacija funkcionirala u braku,

836
00:46:44,300 --> 00:46:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] da moramo čim više

837
00:46:45,460 --> 00:46:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] pričati.

838
00:46:47,900 --> 00:46:48,179
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

839
00:46:48,179 --> 00:46:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali biti nije točno.

840
00:46:50,980 --> 00:46:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo puno više

841
00:46:53,920 --> 00:46:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] slušati.

842
00:46:56,199 --> 00:46:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Bog nam je dao,

843
00:46:59,440 --> 00:47:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] to imamo super primjer iz

844
00:47:01,059 --> 00:47:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] tečaja,

845
