[SPEAKER_01] I on je odmah sa mnom htio ići.

1279
00:56:59,360 --> 00:57:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1280
00:57:00,519 --> 00:57:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] ko bi se s nama družio

1281
00:57:01,619 --> 00:57:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali bi mi išli s prijateljicom na kavu

1282
00:57:03,420 --> 00:57:04,699
[SPEAKER_01] ako bi ona stala nama

1283
00:57:04,699 --> 00:57:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] nekakve naše greške spočitavala,

1284
00:57:06,420 --> 00:57:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] ako bi nam nabijela nos

1285
00:57:07,699 --> 00:57:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] kak smo se obukli,

1286
00:57:08,639 --> 00:57:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] kakav smo,

1287
00:57:09,460 --> 00:57:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1288
00:57:09,860 --> 00:57:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] kakvu smo torbicu kupili,

1289
00:57:11,420 --> 00:57:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] zašto sam ove treće prijateljici rekla ono,

1290
00:57:13,539 --> 00:57:15,219
[SPEAKER_01] zašto nisam bila na kavi s njom

1291
00:57:15,219 --> 00:57:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] tri mjeseca,

1292
00:57:15,980 --> 00:57:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne bi,

1293
00:57:16,960 --> 00:57:18,159
[SPEAKER_01] višla bi tri put i više

1294
00:57:18,159 --> 00:57:19,199
[SPEAKER_01] četvrti put,

1295
00:57:19,199 --> 00:57:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] ako mi nije s tobom ono,

1296
00:57:20,679 --> 00:57:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] ok,

1297
00:57:21,099 --> 00:57:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] onda,

1298
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

1299
00:57:22,739 --> 00:57:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] nekak ne vidim neki smisal.

1300
00:57:24,360 --> 00:57:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je vrlo važno shvatiti

1301
00:57:26,340 --> 00:57:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] i to,

1302
00:57:27,280 --> 00:57:28,559
[SPEAKER_01] i taj dio priče,

1303
00:57:29,119 --> 00:57:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] da muškarac treba to potvrdu,

1304
00:57:32,519 --> 00:57:36,139
[SPEAKER_01] ali onda i on treba dati svoj obol tome.

1305
00:57:36,139 --> 00:57:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ili mi žene ono volimo da,

1306
00:57:38,440 --> 00:57:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] ne sve u kući cakom pakom,

1307
00:57:40,820 --> 00:57:42,719
[SPEAKER_01] a nije, ne može biti,

1308
00:57:42,719 --> 00:57:44,519
[SPEAKER_01] ili živimo u nekom vakumiranom prostoru,

1309
00:57:44,519 --> 00:57:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve to podložno promjenamo,

1310
00:57:47,000 --> 00:57:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] pa smo zapravo često nezadovoljni.

1311
00:57:49,519 --> 00:57:52,320
[SPEAKER_01] I tu usta onda uskačemo jedan drugome,

1312
00:57:52,320 --> 00:57:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] da olakšamo,

1313
00:57:53,260 --> 00:57:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] da rasteretimo taj naš ženski um,

1314
00:57:57,039 --> 00:57:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] koji sva što želi,

1315
00:57:57,920 --> 00:58:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] a ne može tijelo podržati sve ono što um želi.

1316
00:58:01,179 --> 00:58:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, evo, budemo jedni drugima podrška

1317
00:58:03,739 --> 00:58:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] i vidjet ćemo da ćemo imati volje

1318
00:58:05,260 --> 00:58:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] i želje provoditi vremena,

1319
00:58:07,059 --> 00:58:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] vrijeme jedni s drugima.

1320
00:58:08,400 --> 00:58:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna stvar koju bi voljeli naglasiti,

1321
00:58:12,780 --> 00:58:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] već smo to spomenuli,

1322
00:58:13,739 --> 00:58:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] je da, naravno da nije sad ispala

1323
00:58:16,139 --> 00:58:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] da je sve što radimo krivo,

1324
00:58:17,480 --> 00:58:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] ima super stvari koje radimo i tekako,

1325
00:58:20,440 --> 00:58:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali postoji jedan problem

1326
00:58:22,099 --> 00:58:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg često nismo svjesni,

1327
00:58:23,780 --> 00:58:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je ton glasa.

1328
00:58:27,039 --> 00:58:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi možemo biti u pravu,

1329
00:58:29,000 --> 00:58:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] možemo stvarno i kroz neku razumsku,

1330
00:58:33,440 --> 00:58:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] možda i čak i kroz molitvu,

1331
00:58:34,760 --> 00:58:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] dobiti neke stvari

1332
00:58:35,980 --> 00:58:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] i možemo biti sigurni da je to tako,

1333
00:58:38,920 --> 00:58:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] no što se događa,

1334
00:58:40,019 --> 00:58:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] kad nas druga strana ne sasluša,

1335
00:58:42,099 --> 00:58:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] onda često puta povisimo ton.

1336
00:58:44,760 --> 00:58:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što vam želimo reći je,

1337
00:58:45,900 --> 00:58:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] ako ste i u pravu,

1338
00:58:48,059 --> 00:58:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] ako stvari, stvarno s vaše strane jesu u pravu,

1339
00:58:51,119 --> 00:58:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] ako to kažete na grub način,

1340
00:58:53,900 --> 00:58:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] kroz glasan ton,

1341
00:58:56,179 --> 00:58:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] kroz osuđivački način,

1342
00:58:57,880 --> 00:58:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste ubiti u krivu.

1343
00:59:01,099 --> 00:59:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] I dajte recite,

1344
00:59:02,059 --> 00:59:03,820
[SPEAKER_00] ko od nas vole da nas takav način

1345
00:59:03,820 --> 00:59:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] prema nama netko nosi.

1346
00:59:05,159 --> 00:59:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto opet kažem,

1347
00:59:06,820 --> 00:59:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] mi uvijek volimo na takav način,

1348
00:59:08,739 --> 00:59:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] probajte postavljati uvijek stvari,

1349
00:59:10,659 --> 00:59:12,980
[SPEAKER_00] da li bi to što sad ja govorim,

1350
00:59:12,980 --> 00:59:14,679
