1351
00:59:14,679 --> 00:59:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] odgovaralo meni.

1352
00:59:17,380 --> 00:59:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dođi ćemo do toga često puta

1353
00:59:18,800 --> 00:59:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] da mi stavljati se na ne.

1354
00:59:19,699 --> 00:59:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako imamo grub ton,

1355
00:59:21,900 --> 00:59:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] glasan ton,

1356
00:59:22,800 --> 00:59:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] nismo u pravu

1357
00:59:24,880 --> 00:59:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] i kad smo u pravu.

1358
00:59:26,019 --> 00:59:28,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ćemo morati malo projuriti

1359
00:59:28,519 --> 00:59:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] kroz naše teme.

1360
00:59:29,840 --> 00:59:32,059
[SPEAKER_01] O emocionalnom sremniku sam pisala,

1361
00:59:32,059 --> 00:59:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] pričala koliko je važno

1362
00:59:34,400 --> 00:59:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] da on bude napunjen.

1363
00:59:35,559 --> 00:59:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] Njega možemo sporediti

1364
00:59:37,059 --> 00:59:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] sa bankovnim računom.

1365
00:59:38,159 --> 00:59:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ako imamo nešto na računu,

1366
00:59:39,760 --> 00:59:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] ako nam se nešto pokvari,

1367
00:59:40,940 --> 00:59:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] ako nam moramo podići

1368
00:59:41,980 --> 00:59:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] određeni iznos da se računa,

1369
00:59:43,679 --> 00:59:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] još uvijek smo u plusu.

1370
00:59:44,679 --> 00:59:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako smo na nuli ili minus,

1371
00:59:47,380 --> 00:59:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] nešto s računa,

1372
00:59:47,940 --> 00:59:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] idemo još u dublji minus.

1373
00:59:49,199 --> 00:59:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je mi jedni s drugima.

1374
00:59:50,539 --> 00:59:51,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ako se hranimo,

1375
00:59:51,360 --> 00:59:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] ako dajemo jednom drugom

1376
00:59:52,780 --> 00:59:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] ljubavi i poštovanje,

1377
00:59:53,539 --> 00:59:54,280
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo u plusu.

1378
00:59:54,280 --> 00:59:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] I kad dođe ludi krug,

1379
00:59:55,579 --> 00:59:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo ga lakše prebroditi.

1380
00:59:57,219 --> 00:59:58,679
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo taj minus i deficit

1381
00:59:58,679 --> 01:00:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] osjetiti u tolikoj mjeri

1382
01:00:00,559 --> 01:00:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] ako smo već napunjeni.

1383
01:00:02,820 --> 01:00:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ako smo ispražnjeni,

1384
01:00:03,880 --> 01:00:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] tonemo još dublje, dublje, dublje.

1385
01:00:05,280 --> 01:00:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je opet potrebno vrijeme

1386
01:00:06,980 --> 01:00:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] da bi taj minus nadomjestili.

1387
01:00:09,280 --> 01:00:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što često puta radimo,

1388
01:00:12,059 --> 01:00:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad dođemo u takve situacije,

1389
01:00:14,000 --> 01:00:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] mi funkcioniramo ovako.

1390
01:00:15,340 --> 01:00:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ubiti nisam ja tako ni loš,

1391
01:00:18,519 --> 01:00:20,840
[SPEAKER_00] nego s obzirom da je Ivana takva,

1392
01:00:20,840 --> 01:00:23,699
[SPEAKER_00] ona uzrokuje da sam ja takav u braku.

1393
01:00:23,699 --> 01:00:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da je ona drugačija

1394
01:00:25,659 --> 01:00:27,460
