1395
01:00:27,460 --> 01:00:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi sve bilo super.

1396
01:00:29,559 --> 01:00:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] U drugim neče,

1397
01:00:30,539 --> 01:00:32,840
