1404
01:00:42,119 --> 01:00:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] izlazi iz mene je nešto što je od mene.

1405
01:00:44,440 --> 01:00:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] Reći ću vam jedan primjer.

1406
01:00:45,539 --> 01:00:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako,

1407
01:00:46,699 --> 01:00:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] imamo ružu i tvora.

1408
01:00:48,360 --> 01:00:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mi volimo taj primjer,

1409
01:00:49,400 --> 01:00:50,159
