1410
01:00:50,159 --> 01:00:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1411
01:00:51,199 --> 01:00:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] pritisnite ružu.

1412
01:00:52,820 --> 01:00:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] Što će izaći iz ruže?

1413
01:00:54,019 --> 01:00:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Prekrasan miris.

1414
01:00:56,199 --> 01:00:56,820
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je

1415
