[SPEAKER_00] pritisak uzrokovao

1416
01:01:00,039 --> 01:01:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] u tom smislu da ruža lijepo miriši?

1417
01:01:02,320 --> 01:01:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tehnički ne.

1418
01:01:03,679 --> 01:01:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1419
01:01:03,920 --> 01:01:05,639
[SPEAKER_00] pritisak je

1420
01:01:05,639 --> 01:01:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] samo otkriju

1421
01:01:06,519 --> 01:01:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] unutarnja svojstva ruže.

1422
01:01:07,800 --> 01:01:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Imate tvora.

1423
01:01:09,059 --> 01:01:11,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mu dođemo blizu

1424
01:01:11,280 --> 01:01:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] i pritištamo ga

1425
01:01:12,099 --> 01:01:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu

1426
01:01:12,559 --> 01:01:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] ili ga svedemo kut,

1427
01:01:13,699 --> 01:01:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] ono će znamo što,

1428
01:01:14,679 --> 01:01:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] ispustiti miris.

1429
01:01:15,559 --> 01:01:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je pritisak

1430
01:01:16,739 --> 01:01:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] glavni razlog zašto

1431
01:01:18,039 --> 01:01:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] tvor smrdi?

1432
01:01:19,119 --> 01:01:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1433
01:01:19,480 --> 01:01:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nego je pritisak

1434
01:01:20,960 --> 01:01:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] otkriju unutarnja svojstva

1435
01:01:22,420 --> 01:01:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] što je otvorio.

1436
01:01:23,780 --> 01:01:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] Kada mi

1437
01:01:24,860 --> 01:01:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] u braku

1438
01:01:25,699 --> 01:01:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] držimo pritisak,

1439
01:01:26,960 --> 01:01:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] iz našeg srca

1440
01:01:28,000 --> 01:01:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] izađe ono što je

1441
01:01:28,820 --> 01:01:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] u našem srcu.

1442
01:01:29,500 --> 01:01:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad,

1443
01:01:30,340 --> 01:01:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] može on biti ruža,

1444
01:01:31,320 --> 01:01:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] može on biti i tvorn.

1445
01:01:32,920 --> 01:01:34,780
[SPEAKER_00] I u tako jednoj situaciji

1446
01:01:34,780 --> 01:01:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] bili smo na,

1447
01:01:37,139 --> 01:01:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] sjećam se,

1448
01:01:38,119 --> 01:01:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] jednog ludog kruga

1449
01:01:38,960 --> 01:01:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno ja odlazio

1450
01:01:40,659 --> 01:01:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] na mise

1451
01:01:41,139 --> 01:01:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] tih dana,

1452
01:01:41,960 --> 01:01:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] sve je super,

1453
01:01:43,039 --> 01:01:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] divno, krasno,

1454
01:01:43,639 --> 01:01:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] molim,

1455
01:01:43,920 --> 01:01:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

1456
01:01:44,719 --> 01:01:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] promeni ti moju Ivanu,

1457
01:01:46,039 --> 01:01:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] dajte njoj mudrost,

1458
01:01:48,320 --> 01:01:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] snage,

1459
01:01:48,739 --> 01:01:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] da naš brak procvjeta,

1460
01:01:49,900 --> 01:01:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja sve dobro činim

1461
01:01:51,179 --> 01:01:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam možda baš tako direktno,

1462
01:01:54,219 --> 01:01:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je naš stav srca.

1463
01:01:55,599 --> 01:01:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je naš stav srca.

1464
01:01:57,239 --> 01:01:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Promeni ti nju

1465
01:01:58,460 --> 01:01:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] i dođem ja,

1466
01:01:59,500 --> 01:02:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] sjećam se večer i doma,

1467
01:02:00,519 --> 01:02:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] legnemo krevet u tom ludom krugu

1468
01:02:02,280 --> 01:02:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] i onak,

1469
01:02:03,639 --> 01:02:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] dobro,

1470
01:02:04,199 --> 01:02:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam to da nas učinio,

1471
01:02:05,139 --> 01:02:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] bit će to dobro,

1472
01:02:06,159 --> 01:02:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali nime ja sam zašto je ono tako,

1473
01:02:07,420 --> 01:02:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je ono ovako,

1474
01:02:08,199 --> 01:02:08,900
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je ono ovo,

1475
01:02:08,900 --> 01:02:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] zašto,

1476
01:02:09,199 --> 01:02:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno mi nije jasno,

1477
01:02:10,380 --> 01:02:11,719
[SPEAKER_00] ležemo svaki onako na rubu,

1478
01:02:11,719 --> 01:02:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] je slučajno da se ne bi dotaknulo,

1479
01:02:12,840 --> 01:02:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] već skoro ne opadneš na pot

1480
01:02:14,260 --> 01:02:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] i u jednom čujem glas,

1481
01:02:16,840 --> 01:02:18,639
[SPEAKER_00] što ti radiš?

1482
01:02:21,239 --> 01:02:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] halo,

1483
01:02:21,559 --> 01:02:22,280
[SPEAKER_00] ko pričao?

